{"tid":1200219,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【口吃撚】漏口真係好辛苦","createTime":"2019-06-10T16:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T17:43:27.000Z","uid":205565,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c3b7f0992d93751e19684101fca7cc13ef696941","tid":1200219,"uid":205565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:52:51.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有冇口吃呢個問題呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我自問說話流暢嘅 平時講野都可以流暢咁加插一啲說話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但唔講唔知原來我係<span style=\"color: red;\">緊張</span> 同人<span style=\"color: red;\">二對一</span>咁吹下水個時 又會<span style=\"color: red;\">突發性咁樣口窒窒</span>喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係呢到等我分享下我係點樣處理口吃呢個問題<br />\n<br />\n首先，最緊要係保持你嘅呼吸係流暢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人係識<span style=\"color: red;\">新朋友</span>個時 都比較唔自然得嚟又帶有小小嘅緊張 但唔緊要嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係正常嘅<br />\n深呼吸就可以好有效咁幫你解決呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係吸得快就有用架啦喎 <span style=\"color: red;\">用多小小時間</span>係唔緊要嘅 最緊要係保持到暢通氣道 等你講野都可以穩定啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其次，用一啲身體語言都可以好有效咁幫助你表達<br />\n呢到當然唔係叫你要掂你啲朋友仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我指啲係可能<span style=\"color: red;\">舉高雙手 指手畫腳</span> 等等小動作 雖然咁樣可能會<span style=\"color: red;\">阻礙到佢嘅視線</span> 但唔緊要嘅 傾計最重要都係雙方嘅交流 <br />\n咁做可以幫你穩定一下你嘅情緒 令到你個人比較自信啲 講野都可以流暢啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後，同新朋友傾計係會比較正經小小嘅<br />\n一時之間要你正正經經咁講野係的確有啲難度嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以其實你<span style=\"color: red;\">唔小心講左一兩句說話</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實係唔緊要嘅<br />\n大家都體諒嘅 因為對方都可能會講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以希望呢個時候你都可以<span style=\"color: red;\">保持理智</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好被佢一兩句說話影響左你同佢交朋友嘅想法啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n題外話：其實識到嘅機會真係冇乜<br />\n大家要把握<span style=\"color: red;\">呢啲機會</span> 難得對方有興趣同你傾下計 你咪同佢傾下計囉 唔好介意可能會用<span style=\"color: red;\">對方個小小時間</span> <br />\n始終識朋友都要有返咁上下嘅交流先可以搵到共同話題 我就認為可以 由佢嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">飲食喜好 家庭狀況</span>去入手嘅 適當時候 亦可以<span style=\"color: red;\">問候下佢嘅家人</span> 小小關心可以引起佢嘅好感喔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf7a0f1756920e5d69d29ad02a33913e83f8e39","tid":1200219,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a9ae19c0c10eba44cf0d14998432739bb0400e","tid":1200219,"uid":205565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:54:24.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1077b0e8d3f56b0ef111365accae4e273092f8bc","tid":1200219,"uid":205565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:54:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"7b3fbf69a67d9fa830cb43832e6d6ed2178305ea","tid":1200219,"uid":205565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:54:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"053ace1ccf3df7b79efb59f9806f7e2497ac75a7","tid":1200219,"uid":205565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"pishhshs"},{"pid":"fea440340e389df229f980748e9e887a4c4f5cab","tid":1200219,"uid":205565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T16:55:18.000Z","msg":"希望可以幫到口吃嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor